        <updateDate>2011-09-26T19:30:12Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Former Soviet Union State Pension Fairness Act of 2011 - Directs the Secretary of State and the Commissioner of Social Security to continue to work with the governments of the states of the former Soviet Union to encourage them to adopt policies that would allow receipt of pensions for individuals who worked in any such state and earned a pension and currently reside in the United States.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
